@startuml VehicleMaintenanceLogger_SequenceDiagram
actor User
participant UI
participant API
participant MaintenanceService
participant Database
User -> UI: Log oil change
UI -> API: POST /api/maintenance
API -> MaintenanceService: CreateMaintenanceRecord(serviceData)
MaintenanceService -> Database: Insert MaintenanceRecord
MaintenanceService -> MaintenanceService: CalculateNextServiceDue()
MaintenanceService --> API: Record created
API --> UI: Success
UI --> User: Service logged
@enduml
